GOOD SUFFIC HEURISTIC:
When a mismatch happens after some characters already matched,that matched part is called a Good Suffix
This involves a preprocessing step where a table is generated to optimize the pattern matching process.
When a mismatch occurs, the pattern is shifted based on the following rules:
->Another occurrence of t in P
->Prefix of P matches the suffix of t
->Move the pattern past t

